items.name: NY_Citibike_202401
items.description: New York City has a bike rental program called Citibike sponsored by Citibank and Lyft. There are bike rental stations  scattered throughout the city. The goal of this assignment is to count the number of Citibike trips originating at each station in January 2024.

items.name: Sales_and_Profit_Insights_Project
items.description: This project analyzes a retail sales dataset, transforming raw transaction data into actionable insights. It includes customer demographics, product details, sales transactions, and financial metrics, offering a comprehensive view of sales performance across locations, product categories, and time periods to support business decision-making.
